edBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T19:25:25.000Z","msg":"「佔左先」？<br />\n<br />\n無目標無戰略，我佔屋企涼冷氣唔好"},{"pid":"507f8ea2ac1303fd833a097f597e19ef37a104a9","tid":1249621,"uid":124859,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T19:44:42.000Z","msg":"真係要有個基地玩下<br />\n下下暴曬好難頂<br />\n玩一日又走，佔第二到"},{"pid":"ad3502887223c84d68d90c67488a4599f88aa0de","tid":1249621,"uid":98431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T20:23:34.000Z","msg":"自己睇路 呢兩日三毛不斷想人衝<br />\n<br />\n係人係鬼 我都唔知"},{"pid":"f57e9378cf3625d4234ffec8f1e190506f2ca11b","tid":1249621,"uid":158888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T22:04:48.000Z","msg":"佔立法會先<br />\n立法會放暑假先諗政總"},{"pid":"620f09cae07e4985edc8ea332e0aea1972dbb828","tid":1249621,"uid":266563,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"8b6aad76085ec1761f63316b3ba31f9f50c177a6","tid":1249621,"uid":20058,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"23bdb586c1d01d2ffb71609c84c97afa19876c35","tid":1249621,"uid":69314,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"d1705b69e6ea748b8f427a0c7b05494a7ab06206","tid":1249621,"uid":20058,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T19:08:34.000Z","msg":"重複14年佔中啊<br />\n五年都冇進步<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T19:11:02.000Z","msg":"佔中係道路，政總同立院係重要政治機構，差好遠，你佔路係影響市民，長遠失民心，佔政總立院係侮辱緊佢"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T19:12:34.000Z","msg":"立法會就可以將啲民生議案擺上前<br />\n之後屌柒你哋班柒頭話影響民生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢招泛民拉布都用過<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T22:50:54.000Z","msg":"其實佔領真係可能難啲<br />\n因為狗會圍你<br />\n斷你糧水電<br />\n仲用輿論話你影響民生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然一開始當狗要清我地 市民會支持我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但如果狗唔清場 （分分鐘佢地想咁） 市民既取態之後好難講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">但我認為對付政府不能磨<br />\n我地要以最少消耗達到最大效益<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n既然政府用空城計 <span style=\"color: red;\">將計就計未必差</span><br />\n例如我地沖入去立法會 用噴漆係顯眼位噴下<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">「淋病閱哦食屎狗」<br />\n「香港警察冇冧巴」</span><br />\n仲之就係一堆1）hi佢老母同2）政府暴政同3）政府既砌詞狡辯同4）政府承諾（未閱現）<br />\n越難洗越好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後閃人 咁佢地空城計都耐你唔何<br />\n如果狗係我地入去既時候圍我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n放心 到時候200萬人就出黎 佢地一定龜縮番<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n只要佢一開會就傳媒就影到<br />\n佢講民生咁重要咪開囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果佢突然重提 我地就再上街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n總之消耗戰難打<br />\n但<span style=\"color: red;\">非暴力既速戰速決我地挽得起</span><br />\n因為我地人多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab60488819a51865bcba835348ebce92d5bfdb47","tid":1249621,"uid":264661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8f15cb33dbde248c72bf286c26764de9f30fb509","tid":1249621,"uid":158738,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"05ac36afa3a021fec7874fab7373f972df6c9e68","tid":1249621,"uid":69314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T18:36:16.000Z","msg":"佔左先啦，咁大個地方空城比你佔都唔佔。<br />\n<br />\n洗唔洗咁驚空城計呀<br />\n<br />\n你佔左有個地方做基地做籌碼<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">大家聽日衝立院佔政總<br />\n<br />\n直到G20</span></span>"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T19:18:43.000Z","msg":"樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又講「立院」（立法會）又講「警局」（警署/差館），都唔知係咪香港人嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T23:26:40.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"4c20c32ba7c9386a60e7c46243ec55ee95c984b5","tid":1249621,"uid":17232,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b6280257636b8b041662b02753e06dfcd9cbdbf9","tid":1249621,"uid":68604,"like":6,"dislike":17,"score":-11,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T18:46:06.000Z","msg":"好似今日咁樣叫升級，真係不如收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T01:21:09.000Z","msg":"五毛已block"},{"pid":"80dd0053ddea19f89879b4be84211e90fd6e68e6","tid":1249621,"uid":29474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T02:23:11.000Z","msg":"太陽花運動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c14777a754568d3d1a4ca4a7ba61b1b690bb4f05","tid":1249621,"uid":87985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d408660fa2431ba3d79d863405ad64069ca3d327","tid":1249621,"uid":15846,"like":5,"dislike":5,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b6280257636b8b041662b02753e06dfcd9cbdbf9","tid":1249621,"uid":68604,"like":6,"dislike":17,"score":-11,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T18:46:06.000Z","msg":"好似今日咁樣叫升級，真係不如收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T18:51:29.000Z","msg":"對比612，咁都叫升級真係唔夠膽講出口，係咪掟左幾粒蛋、幫稅務大樓提早兩粒鐘收工就好巴閉，如果係日日幫佢提早收工就話姐"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T02:23:46.000Z","msg":"唔好鬧，今次係有進步"},{"pid":"fdf5dd9e7739d732e9b29995163bb327a33c17bc","tid":1249621,"uid":64743,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"80dd0053ddea19f89879b4be84211e90fd6e68e6","tid":1249621,"uid":29474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T02:23:11.000Z","msg":"太陽花運動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019